;; subaru 昴 — seed connectivity-commons constellation graph (representative engineering estimates)
;; ADR-2606162355 · vocabulary: constellation-ontology (00-contracts/schemas/constellation-ontology.kotoba.edn)
;;
;; SCOPE GUARD (constitutional, G1/G2 — read first):
;;   - subaru is a connectivity COMMONS, NEVER a surveillance / targeting / military-C2 platform.
;;     There is NO :link/inspect / :link/dpi / :user/location / :subscriber/geo / :relay/targeting
;;     attribute here or in the schema, by design. Service is keyed to :service-area (AGGREGATE
;;     region), NEVER to a tracked person.
;;   - G2 no person-tracking / reciprocal-symmetric: subscriber content is E2E-encrypted ciphertext
;;     the constellation routes but cannot read (com.etzhayyim.encrypted, ADR-2605181100).
;;   - G3 cash≡0 / no-ads: :entitlement is :social-security-level-0 (covenantal-universal §1.16) or
;;     :sbt-internal; there is NO :subscription / :ad-supported entitlement, by design.
;;   - G5 stewardship: the occupied shell carries a disposal plan + darksat brightness mitigation.
;;
;; SOURCING: engineering numbers are :representative estimates (G8); ITU/national coordination
;; facts would be :authoritative once cited. Live constellation operation is Council-gated.

[;; ───────────────────────────── constellation + bus ─────────────────────────
 {:organism/id "con.constellation.subaru" :organism/kind :constellation :organism/label "subaru 昴 (connectivity commons)" :constellation/sat-count 648 :constellation/open-bus true :organism/sourcing :representative}
